Implisense event types:
situation (crisis, cyber attack), reorganization (dissolution, merger, aquisition), finances (report, funding, investment), market (sentiment, trade), corporate actions (name change, new product), corporate IT actions (erp, crm), marketing (blogs, awards, sponsoring), management (new ceo, board member change), hiring (job openings), fact (politics, infrastructure)
the size of a company according to the EU SME definition
